<h2>Search Results</h2>

-if @found_pitch.empty?
  <p>No results found. </p>

%table
  %thead
    %tr
      %th Name
      %th Media
      %th Category
      %th Text
      %th
      %th
      %th

  %tbody
    - @found_pitch.each do |pitch|
      %tr
        %td= pitch.name
        %td= pitch.media
        %td= pitch.category
        %td= pitch.text
